content.rendered:
Directed by Gregor Jordan.

Written by Marcia Gardner.

Cast. Dan Spielman. Claire Lovering. Rhys Muldoon. Chris Alosio. Rob Carlton. Max Mayer-Rayment (Tom Macklin). Jonathan Lagudi (Oscar Aruzzi). Cassandra Sorrell (Cindy Yoo). Toby Truslove (Jordan Makepeace). Georgie Oulton (Anna). George Pullar (Ben Barber). Bailey Spalding (Sophie Chalcott). Deepka Ratra (Geri). Abby Dorrian (News Reporter). Kirsty Sturgess (D.S. Meg Driscoll). Orla Saphron (Alex). Nova Onas (Stony face waitress). Laura Brogan Browne (Brynne Matthews). Nick Barraclough (Journalist). Andrea Bornstein (TV Interviewer). Joanne Froggatt (Abigail Crawford). John Bradley (Max Wylie). Gus Murray (Mr. Chacksfield). Davo Hardy (Auslan Interpreter). Daniel Wilson (Nick (Bartender)). Shakriya Tarinyawat (Singaporean Waiter, Party Goer and Conference Attendee (uncredited)). Asiya Ilyasova (Analyst (uncredited)). Robert Alexander Maxwell McCann (Journalist (uncredited))

Language English.

Producers Mike Bullen. Di Hadden. David Maher. David Taylor. Series Casting By. Leigh Pickford. Series Set Decoration by. Glen W. Johnson.

Production Beach Road Pictures. Screen Australia.

No. of Seasons 1

No. of Episodes 6

Status On Going (2023–)
